tweet: At Bitstamp 29% of the whole team - 180 people - have roles in compliance, regulation, legal, risk management or internal audit.  A safe exchange invests in teams to protect customers.  Learn more about what a safe exchange looks like  https://t.co/qRQCAvDqKb #Transparency #crypto
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: If you have any questions or concerns, our 24/7 customer support is available anytime and anywhere.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: Over the years we’ve built up trust - through proven experience - among retail and institutional investors. In fact, our market-leading insurance coverage is one of the many ways we work to ensure our customers' trust that their funds are safe with us.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: In addition, Bitstamp is audited by one of the Big Four accounting firms annually, and we have a proof of reserves initiative underway.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: We have an expansive regulatory footprint in the U.S. underpinned by our Bitlicense in New York, as well as numerous other licenses around the globe.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: Since 2011, Bitstamp has served customers with transparency and an unwavering focus on compliance and fund security.  Bitstamp is widely known to be the most proactive and compliance-forward crypto exchange on the planet.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: Customer funds are held 1:1 in custody or bank accounts and are never lent or repurposed without the customer’s instruction.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: I want to reassure our customers that we have no exposure to FTX or Alameda Research.   At Bitstamp, customer funds are always safe and held separately from corporate funds.
name: Bobby Zagotta

tweet: The recent events at FTX and the aftermath faced by its customers are tough to see. I sympathize with everyone affected, and my hope is that we can all work together to move forward.
name: Bobby Zagotta
